each operation inside the sandbox. Research needed:
  - Exact schema for ~/.claude/settings.json permissions.allow
  - Valid patterns for Bash subcommands (Bash(git:*), Bash(./*.sh)?)
  - Whether Edit/Write/Read take patterns or are global
  - Whether WebFetch(domain:github.com) is the correct pattern
  - Per-project vs user-wide vs session scope
Goal: pre-allow read/edit/write in the project tree, common shell
commands (git, mkdir, chmod, ./scripts), and WebFetch to common docs
sites — since the sandbox itself is the trust boundary.

